topic: Companies Workflow Series ("Trademarks across the world")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for the company or person related to a given trademark
goals.2: Identify the BGP to retrieve types or categories for a given trademark
goals.3: What companies have the largest number of trademarks?
goals.4: What are the types of trademarks, how many trademarks exist for each type?
goals.5: Analyze the number of trademarks across types, companies, and countries
goals.5.1: How many U.S. companies hold trademarks? In which sectors?
goals.5.2: How many people hold or are connected to trademarks? In which role?
goals.5.3: In which sector there is the highest number of trademarks?

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . } LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) wd:Q312 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . }
SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . wd:Q312 wdt:P1056 ?trademark . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . }
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; ?p wd:Q312 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . }

SELECT DISTINCT ?class ?className WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P31 ?class . ?class <http://schema.org/name> ?className . FILTER (REGEX (?className,"human")) } LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName ?ownerName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . } LIMIT 20

SELECT ?trademark ?trademarkName (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?ownerName ; separator = ", ") AS ?owners) WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . } GROUP BY ?trademark ?trademarkName LIMIT 30

1.query: SELECT ?owner ?ownerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?owner ?ownerName ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10

5.1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q312 ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) } LIMIT 20

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?company) AS ?numCompanies WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P17 wd:Q30 . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } }
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName ?o ?oName WHERE { wd:Q312 ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . ?o <http://schema.org/name> ?oName . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) } LIMIT 20

SELECT ?sector ?sectorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?company) AS ?numCompanies WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P17 wd:Q30 ; wdt:P452 ?sector . ?sector <http://schema.org/name> ?sectorName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?sector ?sectorName ORDER BY DESC(?numCompanies) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?sector ?sectorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P452 ?sector . ?sector <http://schema.org/name> ?sectorName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?sector ?sectorName ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10
